Subject: Re: Question for those with popular morality
Message-ID: <1489@quirm.terminus.ericsson.se>
Date: 6 Apr 93 08:48:57 GMT
References: <C4too3.IM7@athena.cs.uga.edu>
Sender: usenet@terminus.ericsson.se
