Subject: Re: NEW BIBLICAL CONTRADICTIONS [Fallaciously] ANSWERED (Judas)
Message-ID: <14644@pogo.wv.tek.com>
Date: 5 Apr 93 17:44:13 GMT
References: <14626@pogo.wv.tek.com> <14628@pogo.wv.tek.com>
