God CANNOT be seen:
        "No man hath seen God at any time." (John 1:18)
        "And he said, Thou canst not see my face; for there shall no man
        see me and live." (Ex. 33:20)
        "Whom no man hath seen nor can see." (1 Tim. 6:16)

Pick what you want!
