Message-ID: <930415.111316.6p9.rusnews.w165w@mantis.co.uk>
Date: 17 Apr 93 21:09:39 GMT
References: <1qcq3f$r05@fido.asd.sgi.com> <1993Apr14.222518.28745@noao.edu>
Organization: Mantis Consultants, Cambridge. UK.
