From: riggs@descartes.etl.army.mil (Bill Riggs)
Newsgroups: sci.skeptic,talk.politics.misc,talk.religion.misc
Subject: Re: Who's next?  Mormons and Jews?
Message-ID: <2003@tecsun1.tec.army.mil>
Date: 20 Apr 93 22:43:00 GMT
References: <1qvk8sINN9vo@clem.handheld.com> <C5rLps.Fr5@world.std.com> <1993Apr20.051902.9472@gw.wmich.edu>
