Date: 20 Apr 1993 17:35:39 GMT
Organization: Sun
Lines: 48
Message-ID: <lt8d3bINNj1g@exodus.Eng.Sun.COM>
References: <C5pr7q.56n@news.cso.uiuc.edu> <19APR93.14322063.0243@VM1.MCGILL.CA> <1qvmk2$csk@morrow.stanford.edu>
