Subject: Re: Who's next? Mormons and Jews?
Message-ID: <viking.735373292@ponderous.cc.iastate.edu>
Date: 21 Apr 93 06:21:32 GMT
References: <1qvfik$6rf@usenet.INS.CWRU.Edu> <1qvh8n$gf4@msuinfo.cl.msu.edu> <mcclaryC5snpq.KB1@netcom.com>
